'''Hulukust''' (s [[tutlayt Talmant|telmaneyt]]: Der Holocaust) (seg [[tagrikt|tegrikt]]: ὁλόκαυστος holókaustos,/ anda ''hólos'' anamek-is: yakk, ''kaustós'' anamek-is: rɣan) akken yettwassen daɣen s '''Šuah''' (si [[tutlayt taɛebrit|thibṛut]]: השואה, anamek-is: arwas) d [[tanɣaɣreft]] i d-yellan deg [[amsenɣi amaḍlan wis 2|umsenɣi amaḍlan wis II]] tegla-d s tmenɣiwt n wazal n 6 n imelyan n [[udayen|wudayen]] n [[Turuft|Uruppa]] sɣur [[Lalman tanazeyt]] d [[iduba n ugellus|temsisiyin-is]] (timura n ugellus). Kra n [[anmezruy|yinmezruyen]] sseqdacen tabadut n Hulukust i wakken ad yegber ula d 5 n yimelyan niḍen n yimdanen ur nelli ara seg wudayen, yettwanɣen daɣen s yifassen n Yinaziyen i wakken ad yuɣal umiḍan ummid n teɣtas azal n 11 n imelyan n yimdanen.<ref name=Evans-NYRB-2015-07-02>[[Richard John Evans]] (July 9, 2015). [https://www.nybooks.com/articles/2015/07/09/concentration-camps-anatomy-hell/ The Anatomy of Hell], ''The New York Review of Books'' {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150919045756/http://www.nybooks.com/articles/archives/2015/jul/09/concentration-camps-anatomy-hell/?utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=NYR+Nazi+camps+Astrid+Lindgren+New+York+police+photographs&utm_content=NYR+Nazi+camps+Astrid+Lindgren+New+York+police+photographs+CID_47ff9b6073315e90ae879838894bcef1&utm_source=Email%20marketing%20software&utm_term=The%20Anatomy%20of%20Hell |date=19 ctember 2015}}</ref> Tamhalt n tenɣi tella-d deg yakk ideggan n [[Lalman tanazeyt]] d tamiwin i d-tehres di Uṛuppa.<ref>Niewyk, Donald L. and Nicosia, Francis R. ''[http://books.google.ca/books?id=lpDTIUklB2MC&pg=PP1&dq=Niewyk,+Donald+L.+The+Columbia+Guide+to+the+Holocaust&sig=4igufxQHRCNrkjwRuMt1if_mf5M#PPA45,M1 The Columbia Guide to the Holocaust]'', [[Columbia University Press]], 2000, pp. 45-52. {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170907033946/https://books.google.ca/books?id=lpDTIUklB2MC&pg=PP1&dq=Niewyk,+Donald+L.+The+Columbia+Guide+to+the+Holocaust&sig=4igufxQHRCNrkjwRuMt1if_mf5M |date=07 ctember 2017}}</ref>

Anhil anazey d yimalalen-is gubṛen-d udayen, yerna nɣan-ten s tarrayt di tallit n [[amsenɣi amaḍlan wis 2|umsenɣi amaḍlan wis II]] i d-yellan gar n [[1941]] d [[1945]], seg yiwet gar tenɣaɣrfin meqren yakk deg umezruy alsan. Asenter (aḥqar) d tmenɣiwt n wudayen yella d amur seg waṭas n usenter d tmenɣiwt s tarrayt i yexdem unagraw [[Adolf Hitler|Hitler]] d imalalen-is mgal n waṭas n tegrawin tisertanin d kra n yiɣerfan aladɣa [[tanɣaɣreft n Iṛumen|iziganen iṛumen]] d yikdawen (imeɛḍar) d inmeglayen isertanen d waṭas niḍen.

